"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"If you’re looking to get involved in the metaverse in some way, shape, or form but you aren’t quite sure how to start, then you’ve arrived at the right place. The metaverse is taking over the world and you’re here because you’ve probably noticed. If you’ve ever experimented with an augmented reality filter on Snapchat or Instagram then you’ve already entered the metaverse in a way. If you’ve ever bought a cryptocurrency or NFT, then you’re deeper in the metaverse than most. If you’ve ever played a game like Axie Infinity or Fornite or Roblox, then you’ve actually been a part of some iteration of a metaverse. \\n\\nFor those who are looking to dive a bit deeper into the metaverse, here are some useful tools to consider.\\n\\n[TheMetaverseJobs.com](https://themetaversejobs.com)\\n\\nWe’ve created a job board for metaverse jobs, with companies like Facebook Reality Labs, Roblox, OpenSea, The Sandbox, Star Atlas, & so many more hiring for jobs in the metaverse. You can easily search for the category of job, like engineering, design, product, operation, sales, & more, and you can also filter by jobs with remote options available. \\n\\n[MetaverseResources.org](https://metaverseresources.org)\\n\\nOur friends at MetaverseResources.org has compiled the definitive list of resources for the metaverse. The collection is categorized by type of resource, such as 3D/virtual spaces, NFTs, avatar creators, fashion in the metaverse, music in the metaverse, and many many more. New metaverse resources are being added weekly.\\n\\n[Discord.gg](https://discord.gg)\\n\\nWith Discord, you’ll have to be invited or find a specific channel or community to join. But there are hundreds of channels dedicated to NFTs, augmented reality, virtual reality, engineering, metaverse gaming, & general technology enthusiasm so you’ll be sure to have plenty of options if you’re looking for more information.\",\"timestamp\":1634591233,\"title\":\"Tools for Entering the Metaverse\"},\"digest\":\"5fLMMwUYde5LsKYV9UgkmjrAkPC3tv2RAWKYKHrwnUs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x223F2db258234F7Fa164a9e4C0929318FEb3B550\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SCWX5re9bb2eh1B19lcBprnqD9If3Uv_tofTF0dSGTA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UGB6CSCCDYJShJOQQwm2Oi7bF2x6IShrhFJvp9mzdNY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"XDNEZeh1fMef0mqNO3L7jxt3cXXEbk70VA0bwyYyBvcYaMUPBQKrSlS00l-V4JSYU1rPOPU6FojNVbiBU4c8Xw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc89e3260a85c228f5dec4a288c9edaf53a833afdf4c7f293ee3f34f3999fd74850eb570e477d34b6ed5710dab9cb39dc3b9caab2f026b6172b2a091794b3afca1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SCWX5re9bb2eh1B19lcBprnqD9If3Uv_tofTF0dSGTA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UGB6CSCCDYJShJOQQwm2Oi7bF2x6IShrhFJvp9mzdNY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"5fLMMwUYde5LsKYV9UgkmjrAkPC3tv2RAWKYKHrwnUs\"}"